Day 1 Morning: We Specters
-Short intro's.
-What is the electromagnetic spectrum? Blue Map - Red Map
 http://www.spectrumatlas.org/spectrum/
 range of wavelengths of electromagnetic radiation.
-Overview of the instruments we will use in our observations some are here:
 http://distressfreq.wordpress.com/instruments/
 VLF, Wide Range Radio Scanner, Trifield Meter, Scrying board, CHDK canon camera + IR pass filter, USRP / gnuradio
 Miliwattmeter, Antennas, Radio transmitters..
-Round for feedback: personal interests/projects.

